channel.description: https://soundcloud.com/razianight/angles-ft-moemx This track took AGES to finish but its mainly due to a lack of free time lately. I wanna thank @moemx for working with me on this track. Honestly, you gave this track a focus and direction that I wouldn't have found otherwise. We built this from my BTC #19 entry and I couldn't be happier with it. Hopefully, some of you enjoy it, and I would definitely appreciate any suggestions or criticisms (everyone is a critic these days lol). Thanks again!
